OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a boy who
OL,7,Fwas sent home from A&E with suspected
OL,8,Ftonsillitis has been adjourned after
OL,9,Fthe court heard he may have had an
OL,10,Funderlying genetic condition.
OL,12,FFive-year-old Yusuf Nazir died at
OL,13,FSheffield Children's Hospital on 23
OL,14,FNovember 2022, eight days after he was
OL,15,Fseen at Rotherham Hospital and
OL,16,Fdischarged with antibiotics.
OL,18,FRelatives arrived at Sheffield
OL,19,FCoroner's Court on Monday for what was
OL,20,Fdue to be a five-day inquest.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FBut, after a morning of discussion,
OL,7,Fassistant coroner Rebecca Connell
OL,8,Fadjourned the hearing for further
OL,9,Finvestigations to take place.
OL,11,FYusuf's family, who believe his death
OL,12,Fwas a result of system failures across
OL,13,Ftwo hospitals and other services, said
OL,14,Fthey were "disappointed" at the last-
OL,15,Fminute decision.
OL,17,FMs Connell told the court a previous
OL,18,Freport into Yusuf's death had raised
OL,19,Fthe possibility he had an extreme
OL,20,Freaction to infection because of an
OL,21,Funderlying genetic condition.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FIt was initially believed that could
OL,7,Fnot be determined conclusively.
OL,9,FBut Ms Connell said a doctor had
OL,10,Fraised the possibility of taking a DNA
OL,11,Fsample from the heel-prick test which
OL,12,Fhe had as a baby.
OL,14,FThe coroner said she would arrange for
OL,15,Fexperts to be consulted over the next
OL,16,Fsteps but warned it could be months
OL,17,Fbefore the inquest resumed and said it
OL,18,Fmay not move the investigation forward.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FThe coroner told Yusuf's family: "I'm
OL,7,Fso sorry we are in this position. I
OL,8,Fcannot apologise enough."
OL,10,FSpeaking outside court Yusuf's uncle,
OL,11,FZaheer Ahmed, said: "It's really,
OL,12,Freally disappointing for the family
OL,13,Ffor everybody to leave things to the
OL,14,Flast minute.
OL,16,F"And being told now about further
OL,17,Ftests for Yusuf to see if he had any
OL,18,Fgenetic conditions, or any further
OL,19,Ftests that need to be done."
OL,26,@nD@bOUpD@YO]sD@UOUxD@AOU{D@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FHe said: "It all should have
OL,7,Frealistically been done when Yusuf
OL,8,Funfortunately passed away."
OL,10,FBut Mr Ahmed thanked the coroner for
OL,11,Fher diligence and said he understood
OL,12,Fwhy the hearing had to be adjourned.
OL,14,FHe said: "If it's going to give us any
OL,15,Fanswers, if it's going to be closer to
OL,16,Fthe answers that we want on how
OL,17,FYusuf's died, it is what we want.
OL,19,F"We just want the truth, whatever it
OL,20,Ftakes."
OL,26,@nD@JOUpD@[O]vD@JOU{D@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FThe family's barrister, Adam Wagner
OL,7,FKC, told reporters: "I just wanted to
OL,8,Fpay tribute to this amazing family."
OL,10,FHe said: "I know they won't stop until
OL,11,Fevery stone has been unturned to find
OL,12,Fthe truth behind the reasons why Yusuf
OL,13,Fdied."
OL,15,F'They've had hope dispelled'
OL,17,FEarlier, Mr Wagner told the coroner:
OL,18,F"This is very distressing for the
OL,19,Ffamily."
OL,26,@oD@UOUpD@dO]rD@JOUuD@FO]zD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FHe said it was "highly regrettable and
OL,7,Firregular that this has happened so
OL,8,Flate in the process".
OL,10,FThe barrister said there was still no
OL,11,Fanswer to the most fundamental
OL,12,Fquestion of why Yusuf died.
OL,14,FHe said: "Children don't generally die
OL,15,Fof tonsillitis."
OL,17,FMr Wagner said the family "do have an
OL,18,Fissue of trust because they have have
OL,19,Fbeen led down so many different paths".
OL,26,@nD@POUpD@TO]vD@JOUwD@PO]yD@[OU{D@fO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FHe said: "They have been given hope.
OL,7,FThey've had hope dispelled."
OL,9,FYusuf, who had asthma, was taken to a
OL,10,FGP with a sore throat and feeling
OL,11,Funwell on 15 November 2022.
OL,13,FHe was prescribed antibiotics by an
OL,14,Fadvanced nurse practitioner.
OL,16,FLater that evening, his parents took
OL,17,Fhim to Rotherham Hospital urgent and
OL,18,Femergency care centre where he was
OL,19,Fseen in the early hours of the morning
OL,20,Fafter a six-hour wait.
OL,26,@nD@JOUoD@\O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FHe was discharged with a diagnosis of
OL,7,Fsevere tonsillitis and an extended
OL,8,Fprescription of antibiotics.
OL,10,FYusuf's family have always said they
OL,11,Fwere told "there are no beds and not
OL,12,Fenough doctors" in the emergency
OL,13,Fdepartment at Rotherham, and that
OL,14,FYusuf should have been admitted and
OL,15,Fgiven intravenous antibiotics.
OL,26,@sD@KOUtD@OO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FTwo days later, Yusuf was given
OL,7,Ffurther antibiotics by his GP for a
OL,8,Fpossible chest infection, but his
OL,9,Ffamily became so concerned they called
OL,10,Fan ambulance and insisted the
OL,11,Fparamedics take him to Sheffield
OL,12,FChildren's Hospital rather than
OL,13,FRotherham.
OL,15,FYusuf was admitted to the intensive
OL,16,Fcare unit on November 21 but developed
OL,17,Fmulti-organ failure and suffered
OL,18,Fseveral cardiac arrests, which he did
OL,19,Fnot survive.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776345056
OL,3,CInquest into death of boy sent home
OL,4,Cfrom hospital adjourned
OL,6,FThe new report published in July 2025
OL,7,Fconcluded: "Our primary finding is
OL,8,Fthat the parental concerns,
OL,9,Fparticularly the mother's instinct
OL,10,Fthat her child was unwell, were
OL,11,Frepeatedly not addressed across
OL,12,Fservices."
OL,14,FIn December, the family met Health
OL,15,FSecretary Wes Streeting in London and
OL,16,Fsaid he was taking their concerns over
OL,17,FYusuf's death "very, very seriously".
OL,26,@oD@LOUtD@JO]yD@OOUyD@dO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
